        This constructs a talk
        Parameters:
        name - The name of the talk
        time - The talk time
        duration - The talk duration(in hours).
        roomNumber - The talk room number
        capacity - This refers to the capacity of the talk.
        requiredComputers - Refers to the amount of computers required for the talk.
        requiredProjector - Refers to whether or not a projector is required for the talk.
        requiredChairs - Refers to number of chairs required for the talk.
        requiredTables - Refers to the number of tables required for the talk.
        creators - Refers to the list of usernames of users that created the talk.
        vipEvent - Refers to whether or not this talk is limited to VIP's only
        speakerName - Refers to the username of the speaker speaking at the talk.
        tag - Refers to the tag of the event.
